<h3 id="at-3-role-based-security-training-l-m-h">AT-3 Role-Based Security Training (L) (M) (H)</h3>
<p>The organization provides role-based security training to personnel with assigned security roles and responsibilities:</p>
<ol type="a">
<li>Before authorizing access to the information system or performing assigned duties;</li>
<li>When required by information system changes; and</li>
<li>[FedRAMP Assignment: at least annually] thereafter.</li>
</ol>

